data.description: This is the one you've been waiting for! This beautiful 3BD 3BA home has an open concept living area accompanied by a spacious kitchen, perfect for hosting friends and family. Large primary suite with private bathroom and walk-in closet. Down in the basement you will find a beautiful solid wood wet bar, the perfect addition to any man cave. Off the basement is a 4 car garage with plenty of storage space and a full bathroom. Several updates throughout. Don't forget the large backyard where you can enjoy peace and quiet on the patio and may even encounter beautiful wildlife. Enjoy all of the amenities that this gated community has to offer while also having the advantage of privacy. Don't miss out on this one of a kind home in Perry Park Golf Resort. Call me today to schedule your showing!
